author: Allan Smith
title: 'Dangerous': Governors decry Trump support of coronavirus protesters
description: "I don’t think it’s helpful to encourage demonstrations and encourage people to go against the president’s own policy," said Maryland Gov. Larry Hogan.
content:
Governors across the country on Sunday criticized President Donald Trump's expression of solidarity with those protesting various state-issued stay-at-home orders, saying his comments are "dangerous" and "don't make any sense."
